data.description: Look no further! This spacious townhome in the gated Westridge Park Condominium is the one. Indulge inside to a welcoming living room and a lovely kitchen that features extensive cabinetry, state-of-the-art built-in appliances, a good sized pantry and glistening counters. The spacious main bedroom is your private retreat, complete with a private bathroom featuring dual sinks and a generous walk-in closet. Experience tranquility in the serene courtyard, furnished with a cozy sitting area - an impeccable spot to sip on your favorite drink and enjoy the outdoors. You'll love and appreciate the community's refreshing pool! It also has a 2 car garage. Conveniently located near the I-10, many restaurants, grocery stores, shops and a gym! Don't miss out on owning this gem.
